lor: red;\">指標：1.有人手持武器踩場 2.有人先郁手(即使無武器) 總括嚟講「被動觸發」</span><br />\n文宣：以武制暴因為多次原告變被告，警狗放走施襲者<br />\n做法：清晰記錄前因，熄機開遮召喚，集中手腳關節(唔致命但手尾長，無血唔血腥)<br />\n<br />\n2.裝修文化<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">指標：1.黑紅藍黃分類 2.只針對大是大非 3.不要無故/突然加入自己喜好目標</span><br />\n文宣：打倒黑勢力，因為目標協助黑社會犯罪<br />\n做法：對準清算名單，裝修裝飾後張貼罪行大字報<br />\n<br />\n戰略篇<br />\n<br />\n1.陣地戰<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">排陣：1.盾及救火 2.近遠攻隊 3.遠攻隊 4.和理非及支援</span><br />\n文宣：對抗警畜打壓集會及遊行自由，保護市民不受警畜濫暴，讓市民安全離開<br />\n做法：1排起防線守TG及彈，2排夾雜近(打狗棒)遠攻(土火魔)防狗推進，3排第二浸遠攻(土魔)保護撒離，4排和理非及支援製造土元素急救品運送到前線...1-3排必須覺醒，未有覺悟請勿做前排，會卡死手足<br />\n<br />\n2.遊擊隊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">排陣：數人為小隊(裝修或魔法組或捉落單)</span><br />\n文宣：對抗黑勢力及癲狂越權警畜<br />\n做法：10分鐘內達到小任務，真正Be water，打亂警畜部署及士氣<br />\n<br />\n生活篇<br />\n<br />\n1.文宣組<br />\n做法：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">必須解釋前因後果</span>，深黃以外好多人唔係緊貼運動發展，一定唔可以本著「運動咗咁耐都知㗎啦」嘅心態，一定要重覆散播各項做法的前因，如跳閘、爆鐵、裝修、神獸...<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"color: red;\">承認責任</span>，波及無辜一定要道歉及承認，絕對唔可以學警畜造假轉移視線，但可留白俾接收者自己思考，例如105火攻或爆鐵，一方面承認所為加上解釋做法及動機，未發生721 831前示威者係排隊買飛，另方面絕不照單全收，如觀塘站，留下時序證據留白等讀者思考，不必一面倒推卸，反而會令人放低立場<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">先後輕重勿失焦</span>，個人認為可守依個法則，政&gt;警&gt;黑&gt;藍，最先放大同攻擊政府問題，順序係警畜 黑社會 藍絲。因為政府係涉及整個大局，警畜涉及知法犯法同濫權，黑勢力涉及傷人，所以有政府先煲政府，政府龜縮無議題就煲警畜<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">本文唔係要討論仲做唔做</span>，例如陣地戰，我都唔建議死守，依樣留待落場前線到時再討論。<span style=\"color: red;\">本文旨在提醒大家各事項指標準則，勿忘初衷！！</span><br />\n<br />\n特別一提再提，文宣絕對不可少不可棄，一定要戒除「要明就明㗎啦」「唔明果d成4個月啦唔會明㗎啦」<span style=\"color: red;\">一嚟打仗要出師有名，對手唔明都做緊俾國際睇，二嚟正如上面講過，除咗深黃有緊貼運動，淺黃中立淺藍都要日日提醒</span>，先有機會令運動更見希望！<br />\n<br />\n大家開放討論同加插<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:08.000Z","msg":"可唔可以整文宣? 想貼街"},{"pid":"fe524a7b1d4bde634e8ef78eeea5fd0beac4c668","tid":1631814,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:19.000Z","msg":"國際輿論開始轉風向：<br />\n<br />\nBBC:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsLzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=b4ff26fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&h=20132a5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548</a><br />\nAnti-government marches in Hong Kong have ended in rioting, with attacks on government offices, a metro station and businesses with ties to mainland China.<br />\n<br />\nCNN:<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsLzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=04052049\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=53844d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html</a><br />\nViolent protests which began Friday stretched into the early hours of Saturday, beyond the midnight deadline when the new anti-mask regulations began. They spread out across the city and soon devolved into violent clashes, with protesters throwing petrol bombs and police responding with pepper spray and tear gas.<br />\n<br />\nUN rights chief :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2Fun-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence%2F&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsLzv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=5d00899a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/</a><br />\nUN human rights chief Michelle Bachelet said Saturday she was &ldquo;troubled&rdquo; by Hong Kong&rsquo;s increasingly violent pro-democracy protests<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fm6HkAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFm6HkAU.jpg&h=cfadcc90&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNQQuuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNQQuuf.jpg&h=e8fe24d4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dkz2kAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdkz2kAV.jpg&h=e42958dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wt3FRHB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWt3FRHB.jpg&h=836cc635&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n開始無人話警察武力不對等，國際開始支持港府。再係咁落去，美國人權及民主法案好可能被否決<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以做多D外國文宣 (Twitter), 唔好覺得有班人會做, 人人都要文宣!!"},{"pid":"22159a78aa91b05419f82529508e600f3a79f7bd","tid":1631814,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:34.000Z","msg":"推，一定要整理再出發！！！<br />\n再咁俾政府帶落去一定輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883027edc724e26e5db0523ed99cbd8b12130abc","tid":1631814,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"推，一定要整理再出發！！！<br />\n再咁俾政府帶落去一定輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3163adada0e98156eb1a863cbe10aa582b2d83f","tid":1631814,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:13.000Z","msg":"推，一定要整理再出發！！！<br />\n再咁俾政府帶落去一定輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79badaf488522ad2f06fd2e47eed5efe1bca1fa9","tid":1631814,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe524a7b1d4bde634e8ef78ee